  "detailed_description": "A 35 part obstacle course that is deceptively simple and infuriatingly obvious in the most difficult way. Your memory, reaction time, hand eye coordination, and critical thinking will all be challenged. You will die hundreds of times before beating this game, because you will fail.<br>The game is the same, but each level provides a new challenge to never let you plateau.<br>Each goal is the same, make it to the other side using only your wit and skill.<br>How you reach it depends entirely on you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TWITCH INTEGRATION</h2><br>The new Twitch Integration lets your viewers become part of the game by raining bits, followers, and subscribers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754540/extras/6aed9705f3464f8a2383ea703bf19247.poster.avif?t=1533145103\" width=482 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754540/extras/6aed9705f3464f8a2383ea703bf19247.webm?t=1533145103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754540/extras/6aed9705f3464f8a2383ea703bf19247.mp4?t=1533145103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
